These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, parkour
2 different pets are kept: horse, frog
There 2 different types of food: lemon, strawberry
1. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Sport         | parkour   | sailing |
| Pet   | horse | frog    |
| Food     | lemon  | strawberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, baseball
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, fonseca
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
2. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Sport      | baseball    | tennis    |
| Birthday   | march | december    |
| Cigar     | prince  | fonseca |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, rock-climbing
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, van
1. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
2. the owner of the snake is not the person driving the van##6
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |        2        |
| Hobby      | baking   | rock-climbing           |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | snake |
| Transport   | van  | subway      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-4::.
