The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, police-officer
There 2 different types of food: pepper, blueberry
1. the person eating blueberry is not to the right of the person traveling to berlin##8
2. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2    |
| City       | berlin  | liverpool   |
| Job       | librarian | police-officer |
| Food   | blueberry    | pepper |

